#: .\effects.json
msgid "Resurrection Sickness"
msgstr "復活虛弱"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Resurrection Sickness'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"Your body is recovering from death. Your limbs are being forcibly stabilized"
" by mysterious energies."
msgstr "你的身體正從死亡中恢復。神秘的力場正強行穩定你的四肢。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Resurrection Sickness'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You feel your body forcibly reconstructing itself!"
msgstr "你感到身體正被強行重構！"

#. ~ Decay message for effect(s) 'Resurrection Sickness'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your body has stabilized."
msgstr "你的身體已穩定下來。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Stability"
msgstr "躍遷穩定"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Stability'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You're fresh from your stay at your sanctuary island.  The intangible miasma"
" of terra firma currently has no effect on you, and you feel fine.  This "
"should last for several hours.  Stay too long, however, and you'll gradually"
" begin to suffer ever-worsening debilitating effects."
msgstr "你剛從庇護島嶼歸來。大地無形的瘴氣目前對你毫無影響，你感覺良好。這種狀態將持續數小時。但若停留過久，你將逐漸遭受日益嚴重的衰弱效應。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Sickness"
msgstr "躍遷不適"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Sickness'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You've overstayed your time earthside.  It's getting hard to concentrate, "
"there's a painful ringing in your ears, and your muscles sting and jolt.  "
"Every action feels delayed.  You need to warp home to refresh yourself, or "
"this is going to get worse.  Probably within just a few hours."
msgstr ""
"你在地面停留過久。注意力難以集中，耳中嗡鳴作痛，肌肉刺痛抽搐。每個動作都感覺延遲。你需要躍遷回家恢復狀態，否則情況會惡化——可能就在幾小時內。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Nausea"
msgstr "躍遷眩暈"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Nausea'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You've stayed earthside too long.  Your body aches and your senses are "
"dulling.  Every step feels like you're walking through thick mud and "
"breathing hot tar.  You should warp home as soon as you can, or this is only"
" going to get worse."
msgstr "你在地面停留太久。身體疼痛，感官遲鈍。每一步都像在泥沼中跋涉，呼吸如同吞嚥熱瀝青。你應儘快躍遷回家，否則只會更糟。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Debilitation"
msgstr "躍遷衰竭"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Debilitation'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You've stayed earthside WAY too long!  Your body barely responds and your "
"senses are slush.  The world itself feels barbed and frayed, and the very "
"air is like breathing fiberglass.  If you want to survive, you need to warp "
"home as soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"你在地面停留得實在太久了！身體幾乎無法響應，感官混沌不清。世界本身彷彿佈滿倒刺且支離破碎，連空氣都像在吸入玻璃纖維。若想活命，必須儘快躍遷回家。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Necrosis"
msgstr "躍遷壞死"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Necrosis'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The very fabric of your being is unraveling!  You're in dire straits.  You "
"need to get back to your sanctuary island NOW!"
msgstr "你的存在本質正在瓦解！你已陷入絕境。必須立刻返回庇護島嶼！"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Disintegration!"
msgstr "躍遷崩解！"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Disintegration!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You're going to die.  And if you weren't busy leaking blood out of every "
"pore, you'd find a better way to emphasize just how badly you're dying.  "
"Your only hope is to return home immediately."
msgstr "你即將死亡。若不是每個毛孔都在滲血，你本可以找到更貼切的形容來強調瀕死之劇痛。唯一的希望是立即回家。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Disintegrating!"
msgstr "正在崩解！"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Disintegrating!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Prolonged warp is destroying you.  You're coming apart."
msgstr "持續的躍遷正在摧毀你。你正在分崩離析。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Disintegrating!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You're being unmade!"
msgstr "你正在被抹除！"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Disintegrating!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The rending of the warp has finally abated.  You feel like you exist again."
msgstr "躍遷的撕裂感終於消退。你感覺自己重新存在了。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Cloak"
msgstr "躍遷斗篷"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Cloak'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You are invisible and incorporeal for a brief time. Now's your chance to get"
" to cover. You also won't take fall damage."
msgstr "你暫時變得隱形且無實體。這是尋找掩護的好機會。同時你不會受到墜落傷害。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Warp Cloak'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp energy envelops you!"
msgstr "躍遷能量包裹了你！"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Warp Cloak'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You fully materialize. You're not invisible anymore!"
msgstr "你完全實體化，不再隱形！"

#. ~ Decay message for effect(s) 'Warp Cloak'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your warpcloak is about to fade away."
msgstr "你的躍遷斗篷即將消散。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warped Omniscience"
msgstr "扭曲全知"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warped Omniscience'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Nothing escapes your sight."
msgstr "萬物皆逃不過你的視線。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Warped Omniscience'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your vision expands until you see everything."
msgstr "你的視野不斷擴展，直至洞察一切。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Warped Omniscience'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your sight returns to normal."
msgstr "你的視力恢復正常。"

#: .\furniture.json .\items.json
msgid "warp obelisk"
msgid_plural "warp obelisks"
msgstr[0] "躍遷方尖碑"

#. ~ Description for warp obelisk
#: .\furniture.json
msgid ""
"A mysterious floating obelisk that pulses with otherworldly energy. You "
"could examine it to initiate a warp expedition."
msgstr "一座散發著異界能量的神秘浮空方尖碑。你可以檢查它以開啟躍遷遠征。"

#: .\furniture.json .\items.json
msgid "return obelisk"
msgid_plural "return obelisks"
msgstr[0] "迴歸方尖碑"

#. ~ Description for return obelisk
#: .\furniture.json
msgid ""
"A mysterious obelisk that can teleport you back home. Examine it to return "
"to the Sky Island."
msgstr "一座能將你傳送回家的神秘方尖碑。檢查它即可返回天空之島。"

#: .\furniture.json
msgid "infinity tree"
msgstr "無限之樹"

#. ~ Description for infinity tree
#: .\furniture.json
msgid ""
"Purple-blue shimmers sparkle around the leaves of this small sapling. New growth seems to spring up in seconds, as if in a timelapse, and yet there never seem to be too many branches. It's always in equilibrium. Its strange nature allows you to push it around like furniture.\n"
"\n"
"The power of this tree allows you to produce raw wooden items from material tokens via the crafting menu. Just one of these could last forever."
msgstr ""
"這株小樹苗的葉片周圍閃爍著紫藍色的微光。新枝椏彷彿在快進中瞬間萌發，卻從未顯得過於茂密——它始終保持著精妙的平衡。其奇異特性讓你能像移動傢俱般推動它。\n"
"\n"
"通過製作菜單，此樹的力量可讓你用材料代幣生產原始木製品。僅此一株便足以永恆供應。"

#: .\furniture.json
msgid "infinity stone"
msgstr "無限之石"

#. ~ Description for infinity stone
#: .\furniture.json
msgid ""
"Wisps of iridescent energy spark around this immense stone like miniature fireworks, leaving behind satisfying showers of pebbles. Clay and soil shift around its base, erupting in slow motion yet never overflowing.\n"
"\n"
"The power of this stone allows you to produce rocks and natural earthen items from material tokens via the crafting menu. Just one of these could last forever."
msgstr ""
"虹彩能量如微型煙花在這塊巨巖表面迸濺，灑下令人滿足的碎石雨。黏土與土壤在其基座周圍緩慢翻湧，如同慢鏡頭下的噴發，卻永不會溢散。\n"
"\n"
"通過製作菜單，此石的力量可讓你用材料代幣生產岩石與天然土製品。僅此一塊便足以永恆供應。"

#: .\furniture.json
msgid "infinity ore"
msgstr "無限礦脈"

#. ~ Description for infinity ore
#: .\furniture.json
msgid ""
"A roiling, rattling mass of ever-churning metal. Flares of purple energy arc around the formless pile like electricity, and in their wake, thin metal rods and struts jut out before disappearing into the half-molten heap which never seems to grow or diminish. Its strange nature allows you to shift it around like furniture.\n"
"\n"
"The power of this ore allows you to produce raw and basic metal items from material tokens via the crafting menu. Just one of these could last forever."
msgstr ""
"一團永不停歇翻騰躁動的金屬聚合體。紫色能量如電弧在這無形堆垛間躍動，所過之處刺出細金屬桿與支柱，又消融於半熔態的礦堆——它既不會增長亦不會消減。其奇異特性讓你能像移動傢俱般推移它。\n"
"\n"
"通過製作菜單，此礦脈的力量可讓你用材料代幣生產原始與基礎金屬製品。僅此一團便足以永恆供應。"

#: .\furniture.json .\heart.lua .\items.json
msgid "Heart of the Island"
msgid_plural "Heart of the Islands"
msgstr[0] "島嶼之心"

#. ~ Description for Heart of the Island
#: .\furniture.json
msgid ""
"A swirling, surreal statue of organic shapes carved from dark stone. In your head, a voice speaks faintly. Despite its massive size, it's surprisingly easy to move around the island.\n"
"\n"
"You can examine it to access services and upgrades."
msgstr ""
"一座由暗色岩石雕琢而成、充滿有機形態的旋渦狀超現實雕像。你腦海中隱約迴響著低語。儘管體積龐大，它卻能輕易在島上移動。\n"
"\n"
"檢查它可獲取服務與升級選項。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Novice"
msgstr "新手"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Adept"
msgstr "熟練"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Master"
msgstr "大師"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Casual"
msgstr "休閒"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Warp pulses every 30 minutes.\n"
"Warp sickness after 4 hours, disintegration after 6 hours.\n"
"More relaxed time limits for activities and reaching the exit."
msgstr ""
"每30分鐘發生一次扭曲脈衝。\n"
"4小時後出現扭曲病，6小時後解體。\n"
"活動和抵達出口的時間限制更寬鬆。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "普通"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Warp pulses every 15 minutes.\n"
"Warp sickness after 2 hours, disintegration after 3 hours.\n"
"The intended way to play."
msgstr ""
"每15分鐘發生一次扭曲脈衝。\n"
"2小時後出現扭曲病，3小時後解體。\n"
"這是推薦的遊玩方式。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Hard"
msgstr "困難"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Warp pulses every 10 minutes.\n"
"Warp sickness after 1 hour 20 minutes, disintegration after 2 hours.\n"
"Strict time limits, must prioritize the exit."
msgstr ""
"每10分鐘發生一次扭曲脈衝。\n"
"1小時20分鐘後出現扭曲病，2小時後解體。\n"
"時間限制嚴格，必須優先考慮出口。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Impossible"
msgstr "不可能"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Warp pulses every 5 minutes.\n"
"Warp sickness after 40 minutes, disintegration after 1 hour.\n"
"Extremely tight time limits, no mercy."
msgstr ""
"每5分鐘發生一次扭曲脈衝。\n"
"40分鐘後出現扭曲病，1小時後解體。\n"
"時間限制極其緊張，毫不留情。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Whole Room"
msgstr "整個房間"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Everything in the extraction room returns with you.\n"
"Resources are generally not a problem if you reach extraction."
msgstr ""
"撤離房間內的所有物品都會隨你返回。\n"
"如果你成功撤離，資源通常不是問題。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Whole Room for a Cost"
msgstr "有代價的整個房間"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Returns the whole room IF you have a Vortex Token.\n"
"Otherwise only personal items return.\n"
"Forces difficult choices about what to bring back."
msgstr ""
"如果你擁有漩渦令牌，則整個房間的物品會返回。\n"
"否則只有個人物品會返回。\n"
"迫使你艱難抉擇帶回什麼。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Self Only"
msgstr "僅自身"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Only what you're carrying returns with you.\n"
"You must always make difficult choices about items."
msgstr ""
"只有你攜帶的物品會隨你返回。\n"
"你必須始終對物品做出艱難抉擇。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Free Warp Focus"
msgstr "免費扭曲專注"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Warp Home Focus works for FREE (reusable, no cost).\n"
"Easiest mode - recommended for casual play.\n"
"Skyward Beacon also works as normal."
msgstr ""
"扭曲歸家專注可免費使用（可重複使用，無消耗）。\n"
"最簡單的模式——推薦用於休閒遊玩。\n"
"天際信標也照常工作。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Warp Focus Costs 1 Shard"
msgstr "扭曲專注消耗1個碎片"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Warp Home Focus costs 1 warp shard each use.\n"
"Cannot use if enemies are within 10 tiles.\n"
"Skyward Beacon also works as normal."
msgstr ""
"每次使用歸家聚焦消耗1個躍遷碎片。\n"
"10格範圍內有敵人時無法使用。\n"
"天際信標也可正常運作。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Skyward Beacon Only"
msgstr "僅限天際信標"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"Only crafted Skyward Beacons work (5 shards each).\n"
"Warp Home Focus does not function.\n"
"The default balanced option."
msgstr ""
"僅製作的天際信標有效（每個消耗5碎片）。\n"
"歸家聚焦無法使用。\n"
"默認平衡選項。"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid "Extraction Only"
msgstr "僅限提取"

#: .\heart.lua
msgid ""
"NO emergency returns work at all.\n"
"Only return obelisks can bring you home.\n"
"Maximum challenge mode."
msgstr ""
"完全無法使用緊急返回。\n"
"只有返回方尖碑能帶你回家。\n"
"極限挑戰模式。"

