#: .\items.json
msgid "sky island warp remote"
msgid_plural "sky island warp remotes"
msgstr[0] "天空島嶼傳送遙控器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sky island warp remote'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A handheld device that can initiate warp expeditions. Debug/testing item "
"only - spawn via debug menu if needed."
msgstr "一種可啟動傳送遠征的手持設備。僅限調試/測試物品——如需使用，請通過調試菜單生成。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "sky island return remote"
msgid_plural "sky island return remotes"
msgstr[0] "天空島嶼返回遙控器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sky island return remote'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A handheld device that can teleport you back to your home location. "
"Debug/testing item only - spawn via debug menu if needed."
msgstr "一種可將你傳送回起始位置的手持設備。僅限調試/測試物品——如需使用，請通過調試菜單生成。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "warp shard"
msgid_plural "warp shards"
msgstr[0] "傳送碎片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'warp shard', 'str_pl': 'warp shards'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A small quantity of airy-thin material that resembles flaked obsidian. It "
"glints with a purplish shimmer that seems to stretch beyond itself and into "
"the air. These shards are the currency of your sanctuary island and can be "
"exchanged for valuable upgrades."
msgstr "少量輕薄如空氣的物質，類似片狀黑曜石。它閃爍著紫光，彷彿能延伸至空氣中。這些碎片是你庇護島嶼的貨幣，可用於兌換寶貴的升級。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "skyisland fake item"
msgid_plural "skyisland fake items"
msgstr[0] "天空島嶼虛擬物品"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skyisland fake item'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"Dummy item for Sky Island furniture. If you see this, then something went "
"wrong."
msgstr "天空島嶼傢俱的佔位物品。如果你看到這個，說明出現了問題。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "material token"
msgid_plural "material tokens"
msgstr[0] "材料代幣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'material token', 'str_pl': 'material tokens'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A very tiny disc-shaped blue wafer. It seems to shift in your grasp, feeling"
" one moment like a grain of sand, then a sharp metal fragment, then a wooden"
" splinter. These miniature tokens are rewarded for surviving a raid, and can"
" be crafted on your island for a large supply of common resources by using "
"infinity nodes as a catalyst."
msgstr ""
"一枚極小的盤狀藍色薄片。它在手中似乎會變化，時而感覺像沙粒，時而像鋒利的金屬碎片，時而又像木屑。這些微型代幣是成功抵禦襲擊的獎勵，可在島嶼上利用無限節點作為催化劑，製作出大量常見資源。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "warped bag"
msgid_plural "warped bags"
msgstr[0] "扭曲揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'warped bag'}
#: .\items.json
msgid "This is a template you shouldn't actually see."
msgstr "這是一個你不應實際看到的模板。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "warped hauler's harness"
msgid_plural "warped hauler's harnesses"
msgstr[0] "扭曲搬運工揹帶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "warped hauler's harness", 'str_pl': "warped
#. hauler's harnesses"}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A looped pair of shimmering blue-black straps that can be worn over the "
"shoulders like a harness. They can snugly fit a single item of nearly any "
"size in comfort, and any burdens carried here feel twice as light. Ideal for"
" squeezing one more bulky item home through the exit when your hands are "
"already full, or even some container packed full of other items! Just beware"
" you don't break your back doing it."
msgstr ""
"一對環狀的閃爍藍黑色帶子，可像揹帶一樣穿戴在肩上。它能舒適地固定幾乎任何尺寸的單件物品，且此處攜帶的負重感覺會輕一半。非常適合在雙手已滿時，再額外擠一件笨重物品回家，甚至可攜帶裝滿其他物品的容器！只是要小心別因此傷到背部。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "warped grass seeds"
msgid_plural "warped grass seeds"
msgstr[0] "扭曲草種"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'warped grass seeds', 'str_pl': 'warped grass
#. seeds'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"While these are certainly imbued with warp, they don't seem to have any "
"supernatural powers beyond just growing quickly. A nice option if you want "
"to re-plant grass on your island, for decoration's sake."
msgstr "雖然這些種子確實蘊含著扭曲之力，但除了快速生長外，似乎並無其他超自然能力。如果你想在島上重新種植草皮作為裝飾，這是個不錯的選擇。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "vortex token"
msgid_plural "vortex tokens"
msgstr[0] "渦流令牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vortex token', 'str_pl': 'vortex tokens'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This irregular purplish lump seems to slowly pull in air even while you hold"
" it in your hand. If you have one with you when you activate the return "
"obelisk and the obelisk is correctly configured, it will drag the entire "
"contents of the room with you back up to your island."
msgstr ""
"這塊不規則的紫色塊狀物即使握在手中，也似乎在緩慢地吸入空氣。如果你在激活迴歸方尖碑時攜帶此物，且方尖碑配置正確，它會將整個房間的內容物一同拖拽回你的島嶼。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "warped animal carrier"
msgid_plural "warped animal carriers"
msgstr[0] "扭曲動物運輸籠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'warped animal carrier'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A hand-sized cage with a shimmering portal at its aperture. Despite being "
"shaped more like a cat carrier, the power of warp enables it to capture "
"creatures far bigger than you. This may be your best bet for bringing "
"animals home to your island sanctuary. Activate to capture an adjacent "
"animal, or to release a carried animal."
msgstr ""
"一個手掌大小的籠子，開口處閃爍著傳送門般的光芒。儘管外形更像貓籠，但扭曲之力使其能捕獲遠比你龐大的生物。這可能是將動物帶回島嶼庇護所的最佳選擇。激活可捕獲相鄰動物，或釋放已攜帶的動物。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Autodoc copyplate (inert)"
msgid_plural "Autodoc copyplates (inert)"
msgstr[0] "自動醫療儀複製板（未激活）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Autodoc copyplate (inert)', 'str_pl': 'Autodoc
#. copyplates (inert)'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This strange obsidian-colored plate is capable of mimicking the advanced "
"tech found within a modern Autodoc, and can be used to create a working copy"
" at your sanctuary. However, it is inert in its current state and must first"
" be imprinted on a working Autodoc. To do so, find an Autodoc during an "
"expedition and activate this item while standing next to it."
msgstr ""
"這塊奇特的黑色石板能模擬現代自動醫療儀的先進技術，用於在庇護所創建可運作的複製品。但當前處於未激活狀態，需先在正常工作的自動醫療儀上刻印。在探險中找到自動醫療儀，站在其旁邊激活此物品即可完成刻印。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Autodoc copyplate (activated)"
msgid_plural "Autodoc copyplates (activated)"
msgstr[0] "自動醫療儀複製板（已激活）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Autodoc copyplate (activated)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Autodoc copyplates (activated)'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"This strange obsidian-colored plate is capable of mimicking the advanced "
"tech found within a modern Autodoc, and can be used to create a working copy"
" at your sanctuary. It has been successfully activated and can be used as "
"the catalyst to create a new Autodoc at a location of your choosing using "
"the construction menu. Requires an adjacent Autodoc Couch to function."
msgstr ""
"這塊奇特的黑色石板能模擬現代自動醫療儀的先進技術，用於在庇護所創建可運作的複製品。它已成功激活，可通過建造菜單作為催化劑，在你選擇的位置創建新的自動醫療儀。需毗鄰自動醫療儀躺椅才能運作。"

