#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nearby infinity ore'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Heart of the Island'}
#: .\items.json
msgid "This is a crafting_pseudo_item. If you have it, something is wrong."
msgstr "這是一個合成偽物品。如果你持有它，說明出現了問題。"

