#. ~ Name for scenario 'Sky Island Warper' for a male character
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scenario_male"
msgid "Sky Island Warper"
msgstr "天空島傳送器"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Sky Island Warper' for a female character
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scenario_female"
msgid "Sky Island Warper"
msgstr "天空島傳送器"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Sky Island Warper' for a male character.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"As if the world ending wasn't enough, it seems some kind of extradimensional"
" powers that be have taken an interest in you. You have been placed on a "
"floating island high above the Earth, safe but isolated. Only by using the "
"reality-bending powers of warp technology can you visit the world below in "
"brief, randomly-targeted excursions. Venture down, gather supplies, and "
"return with only what you can carry to upgrade your home base and your stash"
" over time."
msgstr ""
"彷彿世界末日還不夠，似乎某種跨維度的力量對你產生了興趣。你被安置在地球上方高處的浮空島上，安全但孤立。只有利用傳送技術扭曲現實的力量，你才能通過短暫、隨機定位的遠行訪問下方的世界。冒險下去，收集物資，並僅憑你能攜帶的物品返回，逐步升級你的家園基地和儲備。"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Sky Island Warper' for a female character.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_female"
msgid ""
"As if the world ending wasn't enough, it seems some kind of extradimensional"
" powers that be have taken an interest in you. You have been placed on a "
"floating island high above the Earth, safe but isolated. Only by using the "
"reality-bending powers of warp technology can you visit the world below in "
"brief, randomly-targeted excursions. Venture down, gather supplies, and "
"return with only what you can carry to upgrade your home base and your stash"
" over time."
msgstr ""
"彷彿世界末日還不夠，似乎某種跨維度的力量對你產生了興趣。你被安置在地球上方高處的浮空島上，安全但孤立。只有利用傳送技術扭曲現實的力量，你才能通過短暫、隨機定位的遠行訪問下方的世界。冒險下去，收集物資，並僅憑你能攜帶的物品返回，逐步升級你的家園基地和儲備。"

#. ~ Starting location for scenario 'Sky Island Warper'.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "start_name"
msgid "Sky Island"
msgstr "天空島"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "%d items from the red room were teleported home with you!"
msgstr "%d件來自紅房間的物品隨你傳送回家了！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Quick Expedition"
msgstr "快速遠征"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Normal time limit (2 hours grace). Exits will be close together."
msgstr "正常時間限制（2小時寬限期）。出口將緊密相鄰。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Large Expedition"
msgstr "大型遠征"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Double time limit (4 hours grace). Exits scattered over wider area."
msgstr "雙倍時間限制（4小時寬限期）。出口分散在更廣區域。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Extended Expedition"
msgstr "延長遠征"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Triple time limit (6 hours grace). Exits very far away."
msgstr "三倍時間限制（6小時寬限期）。出口相距甚遠。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Field"
msgstr "田野"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid ""
"Arrive in a barren field. Usually wilderness, but could be an empty lot in "
"town."
msgstr "抵達一片荒蕪田野。通常是荒野，但也可能是城鎮中的空地。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Basement"
msgstr "地下室"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Arrive inside an underground basement. Usually suburbia."
msgstr "抵達地下室內。通常是郊區。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Rooftop"
msgstr "屋頂"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Arrive on a building roof. Usually houses, one story up."
msgstr "抵達建築屋頂。通常是房屋，向上一個樓層。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Science Lab"
msgstr "科學實驗室"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid ""
"Arrive in a subterranean science lab. DANGEROUS! Costs 1 Labs Catalyst. You "
"will be sealed inside - bring an exit strategy!"
msgstr "抵達一處地下科學實驗室。危險！消耗1個實驗室催化劑。你將被封閉在內——請準備好撤離方案！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "You feel reality shift around you..."
msgstr "你感到周圍的現實發生了扭曲……"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Warp energy lifts you into the air!"
msgstr "躍遷能量將你託舉至空中！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Your feet touch the ground as the warp flight fades."
msgstr "隨著躍遷飛行的消退，你的雙腳觸及地面。"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "%d island animal%s returned home safely!"
msgstr "%d只島嶼動物%s安全返回家園！"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "%d warped animal%s arrived at your island!"
msgstr "%d只躍遷動物%s抵達了你的島嶼！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "You are already on an expedition!"
msgstr "你已在探險中！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "ERROR: Could not determine position!"
msgstr "錯誤：無法確定位置！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Select Expedition Type"
msgstr "選擇探險類型"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "%s (reward: %d tokens)"
msgstr "%s（獎勵：%d代幣）"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Warp cancelled."
msgstr "躍遷已取消。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Select Starting Location"
msgstr "選擇起始位置"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid " [No Catalyst]"
msgstr " [無催化劑]"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid " (requires catalyst)"
msgstr "（需要催化劑）"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "The Labs Catalyst crumbles to dust as dimensional barriers part..."
msgstr "實驗室催化劑隨著維度屏障的開啟而化為塵埃……"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Initiating %s to %s..."
msgstr "正在啟動從%s到%s的躍遷……"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Searching for suitable location..."
msgstr "正在搜尋合適的位置……"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Your scouting reveals a %dx%d area around the landing zone."
msgstr "你的偵察揭示了著陸區周圍%dx%d的區域。"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "You arrive at the %s!"
msgstr "你抵達了 %s！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid ""
"Find the red room exit portal to return home before warp sickness kills you."
msgstr "找到紅色房間的出口傳送門，在躍遷病殺死你之前返回家園。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "You are already home!"
msgstr "你已經在家裡了！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "ERROR: Home location not set!"
msgstr "錯誤：家園位置未設置！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Return home?"
msgstr "返回家園？"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Yes, return home"
msgstr "是的，返回家園"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "No, stay"
msgstr "不，留下"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Only items you carry will return with you."
msgstr "只有你攜帶的物品會隨你返回。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Without a Vortex Token, only items you carry will return with you."
msgstr "沒有漩渦令牌，只有你攜帶的物品會隨你返回。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid ""
"The Vortex Token crumbles as it pulls the room's contents into the warp!"
msgstr "漩渦令牌在將房間內容物拖入躍遷時碎裂了！"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "You've returned home safely! Earned %d material tokens."
msgstr "你已安全返回家園！獲得了 %d 枚材料令牌。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "=== RANK UP ==="
msgstr "=== 等級提升 ==="

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "You have survived 20 expeditions and achieved Master rank!"
msgstr "你已成功完成 20 次遠征，達到了大師等級！"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "New features and recipes may now be available."
msgstr "現在可能解鎖了新功能和配方。"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "You have survived 10 expeditions and achieved Adept rank!"
msgstr "你已成功完成 10 次遠征，達到了專家等級！"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "Stats: %d/%d raids completed successfully"
msgstr "統計：成功完成 %d/%d 次突襲"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "Your belongings scatter as reality tears you away..."
msgstr "現實將你撕裂，你的物品散落各處……"

#: .\teleport.lua
#, c-format
msgid "%d warped animal%s lost in the void..."
msgstr "%d 只扭曲動物%s消失在虛空之中……"

#: .\teleport.lua
msgid "You respawn at home, naked and wounded!"
msgstr "你在家園重生，赤身裸體且身負重傷！"

#: .\terrain.json
msgid "open air"
msgstr "露天"

#. ~ Description for open air
#: .\terrain.json
msgid ""
"This is the edge of the island. A metaphysical border stops you from going "
"over the edge yourself, but anything you drop here will be gone forever."
msgstr "這裡是島嶼的邊緣。一道形而上學的邊界阻止你親自越過邊緣，但任何你在此處丟棄的物品都將永遠消失。"

#: .\terrain.json
msgid "warped rock"
msgstr "扭曲岩石"

#. ~ Description for warped rock
#: .\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A sparkly-black stone that's glassy smooth to the touch. Seems "
"indestructible by normal means."
msgstr "一種閃亮的黑色石頭，觸感如玻璃般光滑。似乎無法用常規手段破壞。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Your resistance to the chaos of the warpstream increases. In every future "
"expedition, you will be able to endure an additional warp pulse and stay "
"earthside longer. (9 pulses)"
msgstr "你對扭曲流混沌的抗性提升了。在未來的每次遠征中，你將能額外承受一次扭曲脈衝，並在地面停留更長時間。（9次脈衝）"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Your resistance to the chaos of the warpstream increases. In every future "
"expedition, you will be able to endure an additional warp pulse and stay "
"earthside longer. (10 pulses)"
msgstr "你對扭曲流混沌的抗性提升了。在未來的每次遠征中，你將能額外承受一次扭曲脈衝，並在地面停留更長時間。（10次脈衝）"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Your resistance to the chaos of the warpstream increases. In every future "
"expedition, you will be able to endure an additional warp pulse and stay "
"earthside longer. (11 pulses)"
msgstr "你對扭曲流混沌的抗性提升了。在未來的每次遠征中，你將能額外承受一次扭曲脈衝，並在地面停留更長時間。（11次脈衝）"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Your vision expands. A 3x3 area around your landing zone will be revealed on"
" future expeditions."
msgstr "你的視野擴大了。未來遠征中，你著陸點周圍3x3的區域將被揭示。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Your foresight sharpens. A 5x5 area around your landing zone will be "
"revealed on future expeditions."
msgstr "你的預見力增強了。未來遠征中，你著陸點周圍5x5的區域將被揭示。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"The paths multiply. Two return obelisks will now spawn per expedition, "
"giving you more options to escape."
msgstr "路徑增多了。現在每次遠征將生成兩座返回方尖碑，為你提供更多逃離選項。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Large Expeditions are now available at the warp obelisk. You will have "
"double the grace period before warp sickness sets in."
msgstr "大型遠征現已在扭曲方尖碑處可用。扭曲病發作前的寬限期將延長一倍。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Extended Expeditions are now available. You will have triple the grace "
"period for maximum exploration time."
msgstr "延長遠征現已可用。你將擁有三倍的寬限期，以獲得最大探索時間。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Basement starts are now available at the warp obelisk. You can choose to "
"begin expeditions in underground basements."
msgstr "地下室起點現已在扭曲方尖碑處可用。你可以選擇在地下室開始遠征。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Rooftop starts are now available at the warp obelisk. You can choose to "
"begin expeditions on building rooftops."
msgstr "屋頂起點現已在扭曲方尖碑處可用。你可以選擇在建築屋頂開始遠征。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Lab starts are now available at the warp obelisk. You can choose to begin "
"expeditions in underground science labs. Be warned: you will need a Labs "
"Catalyst each time, and you will start sealed inside!"
msgstr "實驗室起點現已在扭曲方尖碑處可用。你可以選擇在地下科學實驗室開始遠征。請注意：每次都需要一個實驗室催化劑，並且你將從被密封的內部開始！"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Scouting Clairvoyance I unlocked. You will see everything near you for 20 "
"seconds when beginning an expedition."
msgstr "偵察千里眼I已解鎖。開始遠征時，你將看到周圍的一切，持續20秒。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Scouting Clairvoyance II unlocked. You will see everything near you for 60 "
"seconds when beginning an expedition."
msgstr "偵察千里眼II已解鎖。開始遠征時，你將看到周圍的一切，持續60秒。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Expedition Missions unlocked. Every expedition now offers 1 randomly "
"assigned bonus mission, which rewards warp shards on completion."
msgstr "遠征任務已解鎖。每次遠征現在提供1個隨機分配的額外任務，完成時可獲得扭曲碎片獎勵。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Two Missions unlocked. Every expedition now offers 2 randomly assigned bonus"
" missions."
msgstr "雙重任務已解鎖。每次遠征現在提供2個隨機分配的額外任務。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Three Missions unlocked. Every expedition now offers 3 randomly assigned "
"bonus missions."
msgstr "三重任務已解鎖。每次遠征現在提供3個隨機分配的額外任務。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Four Missions unlocked. Every expedition now offers 4 randomly assigned "
"bonus missions."
msgstr "四重任務已解鎖。每次遠征現在提供4個隨機分配的額外任務。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Five Missions unlocked. Every expedition now offers 5 randomly assigned "
"bonus missions."
msgstr "五個任務已解鎖。現在每次遠征都會提供5個隨機分配的獎勵任務。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Harder Missions unlocked. More challenging bonus missions with greater "
"rewards are now available."
msgstr "困難任務已解鎖。現在可進行更具挑戰性且獎勵更豐厚的獎勵任務。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Hardest Missions unlocked. The most dangerous bonus missions with the "
"greatest rewards are now available."
msgstr "極難任務已解鎖。現在可進行最危險且獎勵最豐厚的獎勵任務。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Slaughter Missions unlocked. You will now receive a slaughter mission during"
" each expedition, rewarding warp shards for killing specific types of "
"enemies."
msgstr "屠殺任務已解鎖。現在每次遠征期間你將收到一個屠殺任務，通過擊殺特定類型的敵人來獎勵躍遷碎片。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Landing Flight unlocked. While under the warpcloak effect on landing, you "
"gain the power of flight for 60 seconds."
msgstr "著陸飛行已解鎖。在著陸時處於躍遷斗篷效果下，你將獲得60秒的飛行能力。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Your determination is proven! You have achieved the rank of Adept. Rank "
"challenge complete!"
msgstr "你的決心已得到證明！你已獲得專家等級。等級挑戰完成！"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid ""
"Your mastery is proven! You have achieved the highest rank. Rank challenge "
"complete!"
msgstr "你的精通已得到證明！你已獲得最高等級。等級挑戰完成！"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid "ERROR: Unknown upgrade key: "
msgstr "錯誤：未知升級鍵："

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid "You have already unlocked this upgrade."
msgstr "你已解鎖此升級。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid "=== UPGRADE UNLOCKED ==="
msgstr "=== 升級已解鎖 ==="

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid "You must unlock the previous tier of this upgrade first."
msgstr "你必須先解鎖此升級的前一級。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid "You need at least 10 successful expeditions to use this."
msgstr "你需要至少10次成功的遠征才能使用此功能。"

#: .\upgrades.lua
msgid "You need at least 20 successful expeditions to use this."
msgstr "你需要至少20次成功的遠征才能使用此功能。"

#: .\vehicles.json
